            <li>In a recipe, the ratio of cups of flour to cups of sugar is 2:1. If you want to make a half batch of the recipe and the full recipe requires 4 cups of flour, how many cups of sugar will you need?</li>
            <li>Assume that a class's grading scheme consists of assignments worth 10%, the better midterm is worth 30%, the other midterm is worth 20%, and the final exam is worth 40%. If a student got 85% on the assignments, 80% on their better midterm, 70% on the other midterm, and they want to get an overall mark of 80%, what do they need to score on the final exam?</li>
